               <p>I am a <rs id="t17900526-49-viclabel227" type="occupation">salesman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-49-victim484 t17900526-49-viclabel227"></join> at Leadenhall. On<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179005260048"></xptr>Saturday, the 8th of May, between eleven and twelve, I was going along <placeName id="t17900526-49-crimeloc228">Leaden-hall-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17900526-49-crimeloc228" type="placeName" value="Leaden-hall-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17900526-49-crimeloc228" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-49-off226 t17900526-49-crimeloc228"></join>: I felt a person, and put my hand to my pocket: a gentleman said, that is him, in the blue jacket; I pursued him, and saw him put the handkerchief under his waistcoat; I catched him, and he put it down into his breeches: the man who is here came to my assistance: he stripped himself. Dormer took the handkerchief from him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900526-49-person486">
                  CHARLES
                   DORMER
               <interp inst="t17900526-49-person486" type="surname" value="DORMER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900526-49-person486" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900526-49-person486" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am an officer. I was going along Leadenhall-street: I saw the prosecutor challenging the prisoner; and the prisoner stripped off his waistcoat; and I pulled the handkerchief out of his breeches.</p>
               <p>(Produced and deposed to.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I know nothing about it: I have no witnesses.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900526-49-verdict229" type="verdictDescription">
